# TypeScript / React

- Functional components with explicit props interfaces.
- Zustand for global state; keep components thin.
- Match existing Tailwind utility patterns and CSS variables in `src/index.css`.
- Prefer minimal diffs; reuse existing services (`contextOntology`, `agentService`, `harnessService`).
